      • getEffectiveAssertionStatus

        public static ThreeState getEffectiveAssertionStatus(com.sun.jdi.Location location)
        Parameters:
        location - location to get the assertion status for
        Returns:
        the effective assertion status at given code location: ThreeState.YES means assertions are enabled ThreeState.NO means assertions are disabled ThreeState.UNSURE means there are no assertions in the current class, so the status was not requested by the runtime
